title: Anthony Jeselnik | Late Night Writer Dina Gusovsky on Why Everyone Should Be Raised By Immigrants
description:
Late Night writer Dina Gusovsky compares her experiences being raised by immigrant parents with American "snowplow parenting."

Then, Seth talks to comedian and writer Anthony Jeselnik, who also takes a few more questions backstage at Studio 8G.
